<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<body>
        <%- include('partials/header') %>
 
          <% if (typeof redirect !== 'undefined' && redirect) { %>
            <script>
              setTimeout(() => {
                window.location.href = '/dashboard';
              }, 1000); // Redirect after 1 second
            </script>
          <% } %>
   
            <!-- Appointment Start -->
            <div class="container-fluid py-5">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row gx-5">
                        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <h5 class="d-inline-block text-primary text-uppercase border-bottom border-5">
                                    Appointment</h5>
                                <h1 class="display-4">Make An Appointment For Your Family</h1>
                            </div>
                            <p class="mb-5">
                                At HealingNet, scheduling an appointment has never been easier. Our
                                user-friendly online platform allows you to book appointments at your
                                convenience, ensuring that you can access the care you need without the
                                hassle of traditional office visits. Hereâ€™s how you can quickly and
                                efficiently book your appointment: <br><br>

                                1. Choose Your Service:
                                Select from a range of services like emergency care, routine check-ups,
                                or specialist consultations.<br><br>

                                2. Select a Provider:
                                Browse our network of qualified healthcare professionals. Review their
                                profiles and choose one that suits your needs.<br><br>

                                3. Pick a Date and Time:
                                Check real-time availability and select a date and time that fits your
                                schedule, including weekends.<br><br>

                                4. Enter Your Information:
                                Provide your name, contact details, and any relevant medical history to
                                prepare for your appointment.<br>
                                <br>
                                5. Confirmation and Reminders:
                                Receive a confirmation email and reminders as your appointment
                                approaches.<br><br>

                                6. Connect with Your Provider:
                                On the appointment day, log into your HealingNet account and follow the
                                link to start your secure video consultation.
                            </p>
                            <a class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill py-3 px-5 me-3" href="/search">Find
                                Doctor</a>
                            <!-- <a class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill py-3 px-5" href="">Read More</a> -->
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="bg-light text-center rounded p-5">
                                <h1 class="mb-4">Book An Appointment</h1>
                                <form action="/auth/appointment" method="POST">
                                    <div class="row g-3">
                                        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                            <input name="Illness" type="text" class="form-control bg-white border-0"
                                                placeholder="Your Illness" id="illness_Select" onchange="updateDoctors()" style="height: 55px;" required>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                            <select name="doctor" class="form-select bg-white border-0"
                                                id="doctorSelect" style="height: 55px;" required>
                                                <option selected>Select Doctor</option>
                                                <!-- Doctor options will be populated here -->
                                            </select>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                            <input name="fullname" type="text" class="form-control bg-white border-0"
                                                placeholder="Your Name" style="height: 55px;" required>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                            <input name="email" type="email" class="form-control bg-white border-0"
                                                placeholder="Your Email" style="height: 55px;" required>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                            <div class="date" id="date" data-target-input="nearest">
                                                <input type="date" name="appointment_date"
                                                    class="form-control bg-white border-0 datetimepicker-input"
                                                    placeholder="Date" style="height: 55px;" required>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                            <div class="time" id="time" data-target-input="nearest">
                                                <input type="time" name="appointment_time"
                                                    class="form-control bg-white border-0 datetimepicker-input"
                                                    placeholder="Time" style="height: 55px;" required>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-12">
                                            <button class="btn btn-primary w-100 py-3" type="submit">Make An
                                                Appointment</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Appointment End -->
            <%- include('partials/footer') %>
                <script src="/js/appoint.js"></script>
    </body>

</html>